thread.title: Mark

author: Mark
title: Mark
text: As a landlord I have had the most professional property management service from Ms Madeleine Cahill at 140 Regent St Preston for my property in Reservoir. Madeleine has been attentive to my requirements and provides a professional and efficient service on all matters and has worked diligently with the tenants that has cemented a positive working relationship between myself and the tenants. The inspection reports have given me a confidence that the property is being actively managed and any matters are immediately brought to my attention.
